### Describe the bug
When running GenAPI and specifying  `--include-visible-outside` attributes defined by the compiler are emitted.

### To Reproduce
```
dotnet tool install Microsoft.DotNet.GenAPI.Tool --prerelease
dotnet genapi --assembly "C:\Program Files\dotnet\packs\Microsoft.NETCore.App.Ref\7.0.5\ref\net7.0\System.Linq.dll" --include-visible-outside
```

