### Further technical details
I discovered this when looking at https://github.com/dotnet/sdk/issues/32119#issuecomment-1529073358.  I modified the GenAPI tests to emit an assembly to memory and reload it (rather than operating on the IAssemblySymbol from the original compilation) and I found every test that included internals would fail since these compiler generated types were emitted.
